(83, 1, '2015-04-12 14:53:39', '2015-04-12 17:53:39', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://ccbeucaraguatatuba.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/mesa-coelho-pascoa.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-333\" src=\"http://ccbeucaraguatatuba.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/mesa-coelho-pascoa.jpg?w=300\" alt=\"mesa-coelho-pascoa\" width=\"300\" height=\"186\" /></a></p>\r\nJesus Christ  died on Friday and three days later he ressurrected on Sunday. In Brazil, families hide Easter eggs so that their children can look for them. they share eggs with everyone. the children believe that the Easter Bunny is responsible for hiding the eggs, it\'s really funny. <a href=\"http://ccbeucaraguatatuba.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/happy-easter-jesus-21303245-231-248.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-337\" src=\"http://ccbeucaraguatatuba.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/happy-easter-jesus-21303245-231-248.jpg\" alt=\"Happy-Easter-jesus-21303245-231-248\" width=\"231\" height=\"248\" /></a>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">By: Engage 1  - Teacher Suzana</h4>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Páscoa</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://ccbeucaraguatatuba.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/mesa-coelho-pascoa.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-333\" src=\"http://ccbeucaraguatatuba.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/mesa-coelho-pascoa.jpg?w=300\" alt=\"mesa-coelho-pascoa\" width=\"300\" height=\"186\" /></a> Jesus Cristo morreu num sexta-feira e três dias depois ressuscitou, no domingo. No Brasil, as famílias escondem ovos de páscoa para que as crianças possam procurar por eles. Eles compartilham ovos com todos. As crianças acreditam que o coelho da páscoa é responsável por esconder os ovos, é muito divertido. <a href=\"http://ccbeucaraguatatuba.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/happy-easter-jesus-21303245-231-248.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-337 size-full\" src=\"http://ccbeucaraguatatuba.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2015